description: Removes the specified tags from the user. For more information about tagging, see Tagging IAM resources in the IAM User Guide.

parameters.name: UserName
parameters.description: The name of the IAM user from which you want to remove tags. This parameter allows (through its regex pattern) a string of characters consisting of upper and lowercase alphanumeric characters with no spaces. You can also include any of the following characters: _+=,.@-

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A list of key names as a simple array of strings. The tags with matching keys are removed from the specified user. (string) ---
